title: The incentive FSI given on this account will be over and above the Zonal (basic) FSI permissible under any other provisions of DCPR
clause_text: The incentive FSI given on this account will be over and above the Zonal (basic) FSI permissible under any other provisions of DCPR. This incentive FSI shall be allowed to be used on the same plot in conformity with DCPR/DP, within the overall cap/limit of total maximum permissible FSI as given at (vii) below.
section: 33(18) Development of Multi Storey Public Parking Lots (PPL):
